item.title: About
item.description: About Me I’m a senior at VNUHCM – High school for the Gifted. As a student who is passionate of Neuroscience and neurodegenerative diseases in particular, I aspire to take part in projects, research courses and summer camps related to the field. I also interested in computer sciences and have already self-taught Python for over a year. Education High School for the Gifted, HCMC, Vietnam Aug 2020 - Dec 2023 Honors Class, Biology GPA: 8.
